Identifier &#34;Marble Mouse&#34;
MatchProduct &#34;Logitech USB Trackball&#34;
Driver &#34;libinput&#34;
Option &#34;ScrollMethod&#34; &#34;button&#34;
Option &#34;ScrollButton&#34; &#34;8&#34;
#Option &#34;ScrollButton&#34; &#34;9&#34; #left handed scrolling
